  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package conforms to the Minimal profile; a content hash is provided for reference but no digital signature is present. Full 13-factor assessment is included. Decision: Accepted for illustrative minimal-profile packaging purposes.",
